    Robust parameter estimation for the Gamma distribution. Based on the Median and Median absolute deviation from Median (MAD). Reference:

    J. Chen and H. Rubin
    Bounds for the difference between median and mean of Gamma and Poisson distributions
    In: Statist. Probab. Lett., 4 , 281â€“283.
